Package: piragua
Title: Streamflow and Trend Analysis Tools for the PIRAGUA Project
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Santiago", "BeguerÃ­a", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "santiago.begueria@csic.es"))
Description: Functions to compute streamflow indicators, perform trend analyses, 
    and generate graphical summaries for observed and modelled data in the 
    Pyrenean region. Includes routines for annual and monthly summaries, 
    trend estimation (Yue-Pilon method), and automated plotting.
